            <p>We aim to provide interactive education that combines traditional handicraft learning with digital media technologies to offer a comprehensive and innovative educational experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
            <h3>02</h3>
            <h4>Design Projects</h4>
            <p>Supporting users in developing their manual and creative skills, and encouraging them to start their own projects.</p>
        </div>
